query:
with ctx as (
                 insert into auth_core.user_contexts (ip, user_agent)
                 values ($2, $3)
                 on conflict (ip, user_agent) do update set ip = excluded.ip
                 returning id
             )
             insert into auth_core.login_attempts (user_id, user_context_id, status)
             select $1, id, $4 from ctx
             returning *
